high_descs: Turn left and then head left and turn around to face the counter.
Pick the sponge up off the counter.
Turn left and then right and walk to the counter to the right of the stove.
Place the sponge in the pot on the counter.
Pick up the pot.
Take two steps to the left.
Place the pot in the left hand bottom cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with a sponge in it in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left 90 degrees and go towards the wall. At the wall, turn left and go as far as the door on the right. At the door, turn left and go between the two stools to face the kitchen island.
Pick up the green and yellow sponge from the kitchen island.
Turn around to your left to face the door, then turn to your right, moving around the island until you come to the sink, then turn left and go to the counter to the right of the stove.
Put the sponge into the saucepan on the counter in front of you, so that the yellow surface of the sponge is facing you.
Pick up the saucepan.
Carry the saucepan to the cabinet on the left side of the stove.
Open the cabinet door; place the saucepan in the cabinet and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place saucepan with sponge in it into the cabinet to the left of the stove.

high_descs: Turn left then turn left again and face the table on your left.
Grab the green sponge that is in front of the glass container.
Turn around then head right and turn right again and face to the left of the sink.
Put the sponge in the pot.
Pick the pot off of the counter.
Turn around, head to the right, then turn to face the oven.
Place the pot inside of the lower left cabinet then close it.
anns.task_desc: Grab the sponge, place it in the pot, then put the pot away.
